description:
I like watching sonic underground in my free time, so I decided. Hey, why don't I record some of this ****? I know many people would pay to have the experience of watching sonic underground with me, but I'm nice and decided to give you all this experience for free.

As I am the only sonic underground fan left I felt that this is the least I could do to spread awareness about how great and how many sonic underground amvs are out there. I'm sure I'm the only one on earth who loves sonic underground enough to actually seek out sonic underground and it pains me to know that there are very few, if any, other people who do the same.

If you ever get the time, make sure to go check out all the great sonic underground amvs that people have made, and like and support those amazing creators. Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe and also consider supporting me on patreon.My goal is to bring back sonic underground and show people just how great of a cartoon it was and why it didn't deserve to be cancelled.
https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
